title: In Windsor, Some See Family Drama in the Andrew Accusations
summary_full: “Her children have let her down,” said one woman, referring to Queen Elizabeth II. Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor’s fall from grace drew strong reactions from some. Others said they just did not care.
